00:02:25.660 --> 00:02:28.120
When you're out snorkeling or diving to the bottom of the ocean,

00:02:28.120 --> 00:02:32.080
you're going to see some really amazing things, but your ears are going to start hurting like crazy as well.

00:02:32.540 --> 00:02:34.960
This is because the air in your head is being compressed.

00:02:35.560 --> 00:02:38.060
Plug your nose, and gently blow into it as you do.

00:02:38.060 --> 00:02:41.920
This will force air into your eustachian tubes and help equalize the pressure

00:02:41.920 --> 00:02:45.820
so you can dive down even further without pain, and without causing any damage.

00:02:47.360 --> 00:02:50.180
Walking around barefoot on a sandy beach is very relaxing,

00:02:50.180 --> 00:02:52.100
but you're quickly going to find the bottoms of your feet

00:02:52.100 --> 00:02:55.220
