00:03:00.360 --> 00:03:02.940
Then use string or rubber bands to tie it into a ball

00:03:02.940 --> 00:03:06.220
and you've just created a super sand remover that will seem to work miracles.

00:03:06.580 --> 00:03:08.280
Tap it to your skin and it releases

00:03:08.280 --> 00:03:12.120
